00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:36,900
R volarye.

497
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:40,300
No, es Valey Forge.

498
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:42,580
Valey Forge, no lo
tengo en la computadora.

499
